desc: Kustom Kulture Canada is a wholesaler and distributor to head shops and dispensaries world-wide. Sign-up for an account for your store and we will enhance your business's shopping experience with our wide selection of vaporizers, pipes, bongs and rigs.

layout.text: Fresh Sesh Bong Care Solution is the newest advancement in bong care. Infuse your bong water with Fresh Sesh to reduce resin build up and add a pleasant aroma to your smoke. With a wide range of refreshing scents to choose from there is something for everyone.
